WEBVTT

00:00:01.207 --> 00:00:09.347
Today is Shivratri and in Shivratri we
are going to worship Lord Shiva.

00:00:14.501 --> 00:00:33.011
On the outside, we are our body and its
various aspects like mind, ego, intellect
etc.

00:00:37.418 --> 00:00:49.428
All these are outside and in the
outer realm we can control them.

00:00:50.548 --> 00:01:07.418
Similarly, whatever is created in the
universe,

00:01:08.290 --> 00:01:13.985
we can know it and we can
put it to use.

00:01:15.319 --> 00:01:29.629
In the same way, whatever elements
are there in the Earth, and whatever
grows out of it, we can use them.

00:01:32.768 --> 00:01:46.238
We can gain complete supremacy
over all this. But all this is an outside
covering.

00:01:50.514 --> 00:02:07.344
What we are within, is the Spirit.
Whatever is outside is mortal.

00:02:09.376 --> 00:02:18.116
Whatever is born, will die. What
is created, will be destroyed.

00:02:19.969 --> 00:02:25.929
But within our innermost is our Atma,
who is our Shiva,

00:02:26.168 --> 00:02:38.638
which is a reflection of Sadashiva,
it is indestructible, selfless and
free-spirited.

00:02:40.619 --> 00:02:45.519
It is not wrapped in anything, it is
unblemished.

00:02:52.978 --> 00:03:00.168
By identifying ourselves with that Shiva
or getting illuminated with the Light
of that Shiva,

00:03:01.663 --> 00:03:16.923
we also slowly become ascetic. On the
outside is just a covering.

00:03:18.551 --> 00:03:31.241
It remains as it is. But within the
innermost, is the atma which is
unalterable, indestructible,
immortal.

00:03:32.794 --> 00:03:40.464
It is always emitting light from its
position.

00:03:40.731 --> 00:03:49.151
Then after Self-realization our life
becomes Divine, magnificent and holy.

00:03:54.461 --> 00:03:59.131
Therefore, it is essential for a human
being to attain self realization.

00:03:59.647 --> 00:04:03.317
Without that, we cannot have balance
in our life

00:04:06.311 --> 00:04:14.741
and cannot be truly collective, cannot
have true love.

00:04:16.158 --> 00:04:22.548
And above all, we cannot know the
Truth.

00:04:24.278 --> 00:04:29.748
So, all the knowledge which is called
pure knowledge

00:04:29.944 --> 00:04:37.114
can be understood only in the light of
the Spirit.

00:04:38.556 --> 00:04:44.106
When one becomes enlightened by the
light of the Spirit,

00:04:46.505 --> 00:04:52.275
then his eyes also become pure.
He just watches.

00:04:52.947 --> 00:05:01.767
While watching, he does not get
involved in anything.

00:05:01.767 --> 00:05:10.331
Just by watching, he gets the complete
knowledge of that thing.

