world at large.

00:10:51.106 --> 00:10:58.666
What can be done for people who are
suffering internally and what should be
done about it.

00:10:58.975 --> 00:11:03.115
His whole thinking shifts from self
-interest to these things.

00:11:03.577 --> 00:11:07.847
When he looks at a tree, he thinks

00:11:07.847 --> 00:11:13.480
how beautifully God has made this tree.
If only, I too were so beautiful.

00:11:13.498 --> 00:11:19.888
If only I too, were shade giving so that
people would come and rest in my
shade.

00:11:19.888 --> 00:11:22.813
But I am not like that. I should become
like that

00:11:22.912 --> 00:11:26.992
and then, he begins to sing in praise of
that tree.

00:11:26.992 --> 00:11:31.529
If he sees the Himalayas then he starts
singing praises of the Himalayas.

00:11:31.569 --> 00:11:37.179
But the one who constantly seeks for
self realisation, who does not know his
Spirit,

00:11:37.210 --> 00:11:41.990
will keep singing his own praises,
“That I went to the Himalayas.

00:11:41.990 --> 00:11:46.831
I did this in the Himalayas.Make my
grave in the Himalayas.

00:11:46.831 --> 00:11:53.205
Put the flag of my country in the
Himalayas”.

00:11:53.654 --> 00:12:02.134
Like this there are two levels or two
types of human beings.

00:12:02.487 --> 00:12:09.537
The ones who are Realized souls and by
the Light of the Spirit,

00:12:11.647 --> 00:12:17.377
they see everything.

00:12:18.251 --> 00:12:25.471
They never think that by doing this or
that,

00:12:25.471 --> 00:12:32.748
they will get a great name, or people
will praise them.

00:12:32.892 --> 00:12:41.582
Even if someone kills them, tortures,
deceives

00:12:41.582 --> 00:12:48.230
or criticizes them, they never mind it.

00:12:48.666 --> 00:12:54.146
Like you can see Jesus Christ who was
crucified.

00:12:54.467 --> 00:13:02.627
But while on the cross, he prayed that
“O Lord of the universe,

00:13:02.682 --> 00:13:08.672
forgive them, for they do not know what
mistake they are committing”.

00:13:08.672 --> 00:13:13.942
Because He was concerned that when
these people have tormented Him so
much, don’t know what will happen to
them?

00:13:16.851 --> 00:13:23.681
Anyone who is self-realized, he is
indifferent.

00:13:23.681 --> 00:13:28.474
He has no allurement within him that
this has to happen,

00:13:29.272 --> 00:13:34.692
this has to be done, he does not have
resolve for something.

00:13:35.132 --> 00:13:39.502
If it gets done, fine, If it doesn’t then
also it’s alright.

00:13:40.680 --> 00:13:47.460
And when he does not seek praise or
fame,

00:13:47.715 --> 00:13:53.315
when there is no expectation in him,
he does not get stuck into the whirl of
joy and sorrow.

00:13:54.140 --> 00:13:57.146
The joy and sorrow are identical for him.

00:13:58.668 --> 00:14:03.378
If there is sorrow, he can face that and
if there is joy, he witnesses that also.

00:14:03.429 --> 00:14:06.559
And he understands that it is like day
and night.

00:14:08.967 --> 00:14:14.597
He himself is overwhelmed with joy
because he knows that the spirit
is the source of joy.

00:14:14.893 --> 00:14:20.473
Immersed in the source of bliss.
He does not hanker after anything.

00:14:20.812 --> 00:14:24.162
He never has a longing

00:14:24.162 --> 00:14:28.433
to seize what belongs to others, or to
manipulate things for himself.

00:14:28.433 --> 00:14:30.366
Such thoughts never arise in his mind.

00:14:30.569 --> 00:14:34.189
He never has to control his mind.

00:14:34.189 --> 00:14:40.196
They say that “control your mind,
control your senses.”

00:14:40.196 --> 00:14:43.738
But in his case, everything comes under
complete control.

00:14:43.738 --> 00:14:47.615
He has no desire to control anything,

00:14:47.615 --> 00:14:53.785
he never feels tempted to have
something,” and then dying to get that.

00:14:53.785 --> 00:14:59.809
There are such people who run after
something new as if

00:14:59.809 --> 00:15:03.675
their whole life depends on it and when
they get that,

00:15:03.675 --> 00:15:06.992
then they start running after something
else.

00:15:06.992 --> 00:15:11.801
When they cannot get it, then they feel
so upset about it,

00:15:11.801 --> 00:15:16.339
that they think their whole life is
finished.

00:15:16.691 --> 00:15:23.610
Then the attention of such a person

00:15:24.131 --> 00:15:30.851
is very scared and they are very
cautious and alert about everything.

00:15:30.851 --> 00:15:35.280
But a Realized Soul’s attention is such
that he moves through life knowing
everything. There is so much power in
his attention (Chita) that where his
attention goes,

00:15:35.280 --> 00:15:40.954
it starts working. ‘Chitta’ or attention is
the gift of Shri Brahamdeva.

00:15:42.914 --> 00:15:48.544
When only the Brahma remains of
Brahamdeva,

00:15:50.231 --> 00:15:58.781
then this attention becomes so
powerful, so loving,

00:15:59.361 --> 00:16:05.811
so knowledgeable and so capable,

00:16:06.472 --> 00:16:10.982
that it does its work in a very easy way.

00:16:12.125 --> 00:16:19.715
What it means is that the attention of
such a person becomes one with the
Param Chaitanya or Divine vibrations

00:16:22.710 --> 00:16:26.401
and when oneness with this
paramchaitanya happens,

00:16:26.401 --> 00:16:29.723
then the Param Chaitanya does all the
work.

00:16:29.723 --> 00:16:41.741
So whatever work of this world is to be
done, it is done by the Brahma Shakti,
by the Param Chaitanya.

00:16:42.301 --> 00:16:51.201
When a person is doing these deeds
then at that time he does not think that
he is doing it.

00:16:51.516 --> 00:16:55.506
Does not mean that he has no feeling
about it.

00:16:56.020 --> 00:17:01.128
He just thinks that it is happening. It is
occurring.

00:17:01.128 --> 00:17:05.234
This is getting materialised. It is like to
get to a state of inaction.

00:17:05.234 --> 00:17:11.456
Because Param Chaitanya does
everything and I am just a medium in
between.

00:17:13.130 --> 00:17:17.473
It happens only through the light of the
Spirit. Otherwise it can never happen.

00:17:17.473 --> 00:17:20.841
If a person says, “I do all the work and
leave it to God,”

00:17:20.841 --> 00:17:24.970
it doesn’t happen that way and it is a
lie. One who thinks like that

00:17:24.970 --> 00:17:28.547
is deceiving himself and is standing
upon untruth.

00:17:28.547 --> 00:17:32.366
The truth is that Param Chaitanya is
doing everything

00:17:32.366 --> 00:17:39.372
in a very easy manner. Such beautiful is
its skill and its tactics

00:17:39.372 --> 00:17:43.237
that a person wonders at how it does
its work.

00:17:43.485 --> 00:17:53.805
And When a man accepts that
chaitanya in his huge heart

00:17:56.171 --> 00:18:08.521
in the form of immense faith and his
whole heart,(inaudible)

00:18:08.521 --> 00:18:15.359
his entire being becomes so illuminated
by the power of that Spirit

00:18:15.359 --> 00:18:26.484
that he attains oneness with that subtle
consciousness.

00:18:26.599 --> 00:18:31.240
That oneness is so amazing.

00:18:31.240 --> 00:18:34.921
Many people tell me, “Mother, such a
great miracle happened,

00:18:34.992 --> 00:18:40.912
I merely prayed, and the work was
done! Such a big miracle happened.”

00:18:41.154 --> 00:18:47.794
We do not do any deeds. Param
chaitanya performs all the deeds.

00:18:48.510 --> 00:18:52.600
All deeds are done by Him, it is only our
illusion that makes us think we are
doing them.

00:18:52.600 --> 00:18:56.651
We can only take some dead thing and
make other dead things from it –

00:18:56.651 --> 00:19:00.641
like from silver we make jewellery and
then think what a great thing we have
done.

00:19:00.931 --> 00:19:05.561
But all the living work is done by the
Param Chaitanya

00:19:06.580 --> 00:19:11.290
and this donation of Param chaitanya
that we have received,

00:19:11.800 --> 00:19:18.111
the experience of it is only through
Self-realization.

00:19:18.405 --> 00:19:22.380
Because Param Chaitanya is the Adi
Shakti

00:19:22.380 --> 00:19:30.181
who is the Power of the Desire of Shri
Shiva.It is His light.

00:19:32.900 --> 00:19:40.540
By the grace of this Param Chaitanya
only, you will be doing everything

00:19:40.962 --> 00:19:46.952
and when this happens within you,you
can become wonderful people.
Wonderful.

00:19:48.393 --> 00:19:55.773
But when the feeling comes in you that
“I” am doing this,“I” have done this,

00:19:56.109 --> 00:20:01.290
”I” want to do this or any kind of
forceful thought,whatever it may be

00:20:01.720 --> 00:20:07.730
then it means that you have not yet got
the light of the Spirit within you.

00:20:09.388 --> 00:20:13.408
So, all the work is being done by Param
chaitanya..

00:20:18.186 --> 00:20:21.996
You have entered a state of non-action,
‘akarma’, when you are not doing
anything at all.

00:20:21.996 --> 00:20:25.372
Like if this bulb says that I am giving
electricity, then it is wrong.

00:20:27.843 --> 00:20:34.533
Those who are Realized souls, within
them this Param Chaitanya is doing
everything.

00:20:34.677 --> 00:20:39.477
The one who has made you, given you
shape your body,

00:20:39.477 --> 00:20:43.559
whatever is made is by the blessings of
Param chaitanya.

00:20:43.559 --> 00:20:48.135
After becoming human beings, you
have now become realized souls,After
becoming human beings, you have now
become realized souls,

00:20:48.135 --> 00:20:58.579
So how can such a person be egoistical,

00:21:00.796 --> 00:21:04.376
when he knows that “I can do nothing”.

00:21:05.135 --> 00:21:08.625
Like there is an artist holding a brush in
his hands

00:21:08.625 --> 00:21:13.767
and the brush knows,“I do nothing; it is
the artist who creates.”

00:21:13.767 --> 00:21:20.951
Let me tell you about Krishna, the flute
of Shri Krishna said

00:21:21.583 --> 00:21:28.443
that why do people say, “I am
emanating sound? It is krishna who
plays through me. I am hollow.”

00:21:28.676 --> 00:21:35.336
So this hollowness which is called
egolessness,

00:21:35.336 --> 00:21:42.630
which when gets established within us
fully, then we can think

00:21:42.630 --> 00:21:51.659
that what I thought that ‘I am doing this
work or that work’

00:21:51.659 --> 00:21:58.165
is actually so troublesome.

00:21:58.345 --> 00:22:02.925
Because I was doing this work and ‘I’
did that work

00:22:02.925 --> 00:22:07.609
and it did not produce any result, so I
become very upset.

00:22:09.213 --> 00:22:15.683
So now I did this and got a great name
and it goes to my head.

00:22:18.592 --> 00:22:33.632
But (a Realized Soul knows) “I” have not
done this work,It is all the skill of the
Param Chaitanya, so whatever has
happened is alright.

00:22:33.635 --> 00:22:39.205
Supposing we lost our way, we took the
wrong way.

00:22:40.150 --> 00:22:45.350
At that time one may think that I have
gone the wrong way,it was a big
mistake,

00:22:45.350 --> 00:22:47.378
I should not have come this way.

00:22:47.788 --> 00:22:54.628
But a Realized Soul thinks this had to
happen,it may have been necessary to
go that way, so I am going.

00:22:54.628 --> 00:22:59.366
So he does not feel bad, he is not in
pain.

00:22:59.383 --> 00:23:06.183
He is not going to think, why did I come
this way, had I not come this wayit
would have been better,

00:23:06.183 --> 00:23:10.745
I should not have come the wrong
way.He does not think like that. He says,
“It’s all right”.

00:23:11.164 --> 00:23:17.514
