him and ask, “how is it?”He’ll say, “very
good.”

00:23:17.667 --> 00:23:25.167
Offer him just a little sauce or some
greens and “how was it?” He will
say,“excellent”.

00:23:26.452 --> 00:23:29.822
You might wonder, “What kind of person
is this? He seems to have no sense of
taste –

00:23:29.822 --> 00:23:33.556
whatever you give him, he says it’s very
good!”

00:23:33.556 --> 00:23:40.400
What kind of person is he? You keep
him in a palace and he can live like a
king.

00:23:40.623 --> 00:23:44.353
You keep him in the forests and he will
live there.

00:23:45.123 --> 00:23:48.323
You make him sit on a tree, he will
remain sitting on the tree.

00:23:48.355 --> 00:23:54.175
How can he complain when he knows
that Param Chaitanya itself is moving
him from one place to another,

00:23:54.175 --> 00:23:56.442
then to whom can he complain?

00:23:56.938 --> 00:24:03.698
If you hit him, he will say all right
and if you garland him, he will say all
right.

00:24:04.050 --> 00:24:10.881
No difference is to be seen in both the
situations because the Spirit does not
get attached to anything.

00:24:13.222 --> 00:24:19.992
(Inaudible) He can be, in any kind of
crowd or meeting, he will never be
affected as he is satisfied in his Spirit.
When you get stuck on things like

00:24:19.992 --> 00:24:29.099
“my reputation, I am an important
person, I am inferior or I am highly
respected,”

00:24:29.099 --> 00:24:32.819
then you feel, why did they treat me
this way?

00:24:36.260 --> 00:24:41.157
But in reality, the one who has become
truly content within does not feel such
things at all.

00:24:41.157 --> 00:24:44.020
He remains content in his own Spirit

00:24:44.020 --> 00:24:50.430
He remains content in his own Spirit
– he does not indulge in any
complaints or idle talk.

00:24:51.867 --> 00:24:55.807
When he wants to talk, he talks. When
he doesn’t want to talk, he does not.

00:24:56.317 --> 00:24:58.887
If someone says something, he listens.If
these are words of wisdom,he listens to
it and if they are words of ignorance,
then also he listens to it.

00:24:59.177 --> 00:25:04.917
If these are words of wisdom,

00:25:04.917 --> 00:25:06.734
He knows if it’s ignorance or wisdom.

00:25:06.817 --> 00:25:11.810
Suppose someone asks him, “How are
the people of this community?”

00:25:11.810 --> 00:25:17.780
He will simply say, they are all right,
they have these qualities and these
shortcomings.

00:25:17.780 --> 00:25:24.426
He will just describe them, but he will
never say “I hate them”,I condemn
them, I despise them. Never.

00:25:24.426 --> 00:25:31.246
He will simply say, they are all right,
they have these qualities and these
shortcomings.

00:25:31.246 --> 00:25:36.320
He will just describe them,

00:25:36.477 --> 00:25:45.157
but he will never say “I hate them”,I
condemn them, I despise them. Never.

00:25:45.157 --> 00:25:49.540
He will never utter such words, because
to hate is a sin,

00:25:49.582 --> 00:25:55.892
and he can never commit a sin.
Whatever he does, will be virtue.

00:25:55.892 --> 00:26:01.108
Try to understand that if he has killed
someone.Now the Devi is there, the
Devi has to kill the Bhoots.

00:26:01.108 --> 00:26:06.053
That is not a sin, She has to kill them.If
she does not kill them, then it is sin.

00:26:06.263 --> 00:26:13.223
So he doesn’t miss out on his work.
What he has to do, he does.

00:26:13.223 --> 00:26:16.180
Because Param Chaitanya is killing.
Who am I to kill?

00:26:17.237 --> 00:26:21.857
If param chaitanya wants to kill
someone, it does.

00:26:22.765 --> 00:26:26.615
If param chaitanya says, do this work,
then I do that.

00:26:26.693 --> 00:26:32.203
However, before invoking the name of
Param Chaitanya,one should at least be
one with the Param Chaitanya.

00:26:32.203 --> 00:26:37.145
Otherwise you blame him for acts done
by you,when he is not sitting in your
pocket, is he?

00:26:37.145 --> 00:26:41.535
If you are in that state, and you have
achieved that higher state

00:26:41.535 --> 00:26:46.242
where you are one with Param
Chaitanya.

00:26:46.458 --> 00:26:52.690
Then only whatever you consider
wrong, you can speak against it.

00:26:52.690 --> 00:26:57.104
So many great saints have spoken to so
many people, you are so bad,

00:26:57.104 --> 00:27:00.215
you are so wicked, why do you do like
this.

00:27:00.215 --> 00:27:02.970
They told them everything on their
face, without any fear.

00:27:03.409 --> 00:27:06.639
Because they knew it is the work of
param chaitanya,

00:27:06.639 --> 00:27:08.910
what is there to fear.At the most they
will be jailed for that.

00:27:08.910 --> 00:27:12.300
Socrates was poisoned. Did he fear
anyone?

00:27:12.675 --> 00:27:15.545
He said alright make me drink poison or
any other drink.

00:27:15.545 --> 00:27:20.564
You give him any temptation, or do
whatever,what he considers as truth he
will state that only.

00:27:21.127 --> 00:27:23.957
Because Param Chaitanya only will
make him speak that.

00:27:24.693 --> 00:27:30.893
Whenever he has to speak the truth, he
will only speak the truth and he will be
honest about it.

00:27:33.374 --> 00:27:36.264
His intelligence will be able to identify
every truth

00:27:36.464 --> 00:27:38.952
and will be able to recognize who is
true and who is false.

00:27:38.952 --> 00:27:43.279
His intelligence will be very penetrating.
We can call his intelligence wisdom.

00:27:43.279 --> 00:27:46.236
Because his intelligence is enlightened
by the light of the spirit.

00:27:47.156 --> 00:27:53.516
With one glance, he can identify the
level of anyone

00:27:54.212 --> 00:27:59.962
and then Param Chaitanya informs him
how to fix that person.

00:28:00.365 --> 00:28:04.385
Many times, people tell me, you
shouldn’t have said that

00:28:04.385 --> 00:28:09.005
or you shouldn’t have done that but
later when they see the outcome,

00:28:09.005 --> 00:28:12.413
they agree it was good that you said
it.Had you not said that it would not
have happened.

00:28:15.252 --> 00:28:21.042
So, Param Chaitanya does everything
and gains out of it.

00:28:21.210 --> 00:28:29.440
We cannot even enjoy its results. Param
chaitanya only enjoys its actions.

00:28:29.912 --> 00:28:32.562
We are only watching the Divine play.

00:28:32.600 --> 00:28:40.090
If at all we can enjoy something then it
is only the Divine play of the Spirit.

00:28:40.918 --> 00:28:50.561
Now spirituality is the science of the
Light of the Spirit,its working

00:28:50.561 --> 00:28:55.762
and its Divine play.

00:28:57.548 --> 00:29:04.028
If one truly understands this,

00:29:04.414 --> 00:29:09.104
then he can understand that the
science of this entire creation
emanates from the Spirit

00:29:10.400 --> 00:29:13.540
and till this science becomes a part of
our being,

00:29:13.540 --> 00:29:22.120
the outside science is absolutely
useless, because there is very little
science in that

00:29:22.317 --> 00:29:28.067
and it only explains a little about gross
matter.

00:29:28.067 --> 00:29:36.629
There is no balance, no sociability,
no humanity,

00:29:37.144 --> 00:29:42.404
no love, no art, no poetry,

00:29:42.404 --> 00:29:48.692
no respect.There is nothing human in it.
It is like a question.

00:29:52.826 --> 00:29:59.916
To understand all this, to understand
science also, man needs the Light of
the Spirit.

00:30:00.452 --> 00:30:07.432
you can understand all those
extremities of Science that have not
been revealed so far.

00:30:07.432 --> 00:30:11.515
you can understand all those
extremities of Science that have not
been revealed so far.

00:30:11.515 --> 00:30:14.293
On top of that they ask Me, Mother how
do You know? How do I know?

00:30:14.293 --> 00:30:19.038
I don’t. But everything is known(to Me).

00:30:22.107 --> 00:30:29.687
The one who knows everything, it is not
necessary that He reveals everything to
all.

00:30:30.089 --> 00:30:32.739
Because everyone must know how to
understand it also.

00:30:33.753 --> 00:30:38.133
It is not necessary that He goes on
giving sermons to everyone. Let it be
wherever it is.

00:30:38.155 --> 00:30:41.305
When the time comes,then only one
should explain everything.

00:30:41.575 --> 00:30:47.385
Even in Sahaja Yoga, many people get
upset.

00:30:47.680 --> 00:30:53.090
My father is not in Sahaja yoga, my
mother,

00:30:53.090 --> 00:30:57.466
brother, are not in Sahaja Yoga.Let it be.

00:30:58.209 --> 00:31:04.809
At least you are in Sahaja Yoga. You live
within yourself. Because as much as a
person remains joyful with himself,

00:31:05.226 --> 00:31:09.316
he cannot remain so with anyone else,
because everything is within you.

00:31:10.437 --> 00:31:14.797
To think this(person) is not in it(sahaja
yoga), that(person) is not in it,

00:31:14.797 --> 00:31:19.843
to think like this means that passages
of your heart are still not fully open.

00:31:19.843 --> 00:31:23.890
That’s why we think like that. Those who
are self realised

00:31:23.890 --> 00:31:29.519
are your father, brother, sister, they do
not have any such questions.

00:31:31.665 --> 00:31:37.245
This question arises only for those
people who are still half in darkness
and half in light.

00:31:37.245 --> 00:31:42.764
They keep thinking that my brother is
still caught up in this, my sister is
caught up in that.

00:31:44.742 --> 00:31:49.292
They will come into Sahaja Yoga by
themselves. You cannot force anyone.

00:31:49.665 --> 00:31:53.065
A realized Soul thinks like this.

00:31:53.065 --> 00:32:01.670
He keeps watching everyone and
enjoys it.

00:32:02.482 --> 00:32:05.462
He even enjoys the madness of human
beings

00:32:05.462 --> 00:32:08.372
and also enjoys their wisdom.

00:32:09.128 --> 00:32:13.138
If someone speaks foolishly, then also
he enjoys it

00:32:13.138 --> 00:32:16.797
and if someone speaks sensibly, then
too.

00:32:17.448 --> 00:32:21.338
In everything, he sees the source of joy.

00:32:21.881 --> 00:32:26.156
If someone lives in a demented manner,
then also he feels,

00:32:26.156 --> 00:32:32.492
what a drama this is. Like a playwright
writes about a play

00:32:32.694 --> 00:32:37.004
where they show a demented person
or an angry person is shown

00:32:37.697 --> 00:32:40.897
and he becomes a subject of joke.

00:32:41.257 --> 00:32:50.227
So when a Realized Soul watches an
angry person,then what does he think
immediately,

00:32:50.227 --> 00:32:55.817
wow he is really getting angry. Now he
is getting more angry.

00:32:55.817 --> 00:33:01.429
So far it was only at his agnya chakra
but now it has risen to the sahasrara.

00:33:01.429 --> 00:33:05.700
He keeps wondering what will happen
next

00:33:05.700 --> 00:33:09.333
– yet he does not worry. He starts to
think,

00:33:09.333 --> 00:33:14.979
the way this person’s temper is rising,
his head might just burst.

00:33:14.979 --> 00:33:18.448
Then he calmly says, lets cool down a
bit and then think.

00:33:18.448 --> 00:33:21.057
The other person says leave it. I
understand him.

00:33:21.057 --> 00:33:24.292
He simply says alright, understand it
then. I too understand you.

00:33:24.292 --> 00:33:27.664
And then, just sitting there, if you ask
him to write a play,

00:33:27.664 --> 00:33:32.650
he will create such a humorous one –
portraying human behaviour so vividly
– that you would be rolling on the floor
laughing.

00:33:33.784 --> 00:33:41.134
His sight is not an entangled vision

00:33:41.959 --> 00:33:46.179
but an unstained and pure sight, or a
witness state.

00:33:46.179 --> 00:33:52.199
With that witness state vision, he
picturises society in such a beautiful
way

00:33:52.199 --> 00:33:57.556
that without laughing you cannot think
of any other reaction and say, what a
beautiful picture has been drawn.

00:33:58.171 --> 00:34:04.011
Even in the most serious situations you
can understand that many things

00:34:04.011 --> 00:34:07.475
which appear grave actually

00:34:07.475 --> 00:34:13.402
carry a big hidden message.

00:34:13.408 --> 00:34:17.878
When we witness war, we naturally feel
very anxious

00:34:17.878 --> 00:34:23.575
and we think, what is happening? Why
are innocent, simple people being
killed?

00:34:23.575 --> 00:34:28.453
But if such an anxious state arises in a
self-realized person,

00:34:28.453 --> 00:34:35.610
then that very feeling is
instantaneously communicated to the
Param Chaitanya and then that tyrant
who commits such acts

00:34:35.610 --> 00:34:39.485
he will be taken to task and given due
suitable treatment.

00:34:40.031 --> 00:34:44.561
That anxiety only manifests in a way.

00:34:44.773 --> 00:34:48.103
If something is delightful, that is
perfectly fine.

00:34:48.103 --> 00:34:51.975
But when something is such that makes
you anxious

00:34:51.975 --> 00:34:56.523
then that makes one wonder, why are
such things are taking place? This
should not happen

00:34:56.523 --> 00:35:01.901
and then immediately, its remedial
action happens. Many such things keep
happening in this manner.

00:35:02.411 --> 00:35:08.921
Like I can tell about myself, when I first
went to Russia

00:35:08.921 --> 00:35:15.423
then after staying there for 7-8 days I
returned home,

00:35:15.423 --> 00:35:19.881
and it came up for discussion that
again I have to go back to Russia for
another Sahaja yoga seminar there.

00:35:19.881 --> 00:35:23.170
At My home everyone said, you just
been there

00:35:23.170 --> 00:35:25.925
and again you are going for two or three
days.What’s the point of going again?

00:35:25.925 --> 00:35:28.311
Let it go, there are others who can
handle it.

00:35:28.311 --> 00:35:31.084
But I said: “No, I must go there.

00:35:31.084 --> 00:35:35.001
They asked why? I said, because I have
to break the Eastern Block(countries).

00:35:35.001 --> 00:35:37.506
They asked how will it break? I replied,
“it will just break.”

00:35:37.506 --> 00:35:42.970
People from Eastern Block countries
will come there and when these people
from Eastern Block

00:35:44.599 --> 00:35:52.589
get their Self Realisation and return to
their countries, then the Param
Chaitanya will start working there,

00:35:53.011 --> 00:35:57.561
even if there is only one person from
each of those countries.” The surprising
thing about this is that

00:35:57.561 --> 00:36:01.367
I spoke only for forty-five minutes there
and in the next fifteen minutes,gave
Realization,

00:36:01.367 --> 00:36:05.715
and when these people returned to
their countries, the work got done
there.

00:36:07.105 --> 00:36:13.705
So for the work of Param Chaitanya, it is
necessary that Self-realized people
should be there.

00:36:14.797 --> 00:36:24.957
It is their instrument. The work of Param
Chaitanya gets done through the desire
of Self-realized people.

00:36:25.145 --> 00:36:32.576
If you have a desire, the work can be
done but there should be purity too
in your desire.

00:36:32.576 --> 00:36:39.622
It should not be a desire in which you
are selfish, or a desire in which you
think about yourself only.

00:36:39.622 --> 00:36:47.067
Because this work gets done by the
power of the Spirit. The Atma is our
Shiva,

00:36:47.067 --> 00:36:51.123
who as I have already told you is
absolutely uninhibited, dispassionate,

00:36:52.393 --> 00:37:02.123
formless, unceasing and eternal. It is of
that nature.

00:37:02.717 --> 00:37:11.417
Therefore when a person becomes self
realised, you will find all these qualities
in him.

00:37:11.417 --> 00:37:13.777
If these qualities are not in you, then
like I said

00:37:13.777 --> 00:37:17.980
from the outside you may have all
these covers,

00:37:17.980 --> 00:37:22.634
you may be a king or anything but from
within, you are dispassionate,

00:37:23.157 --> 00:37:28.587
detached, you are not attached to
anything.

00:37:28.666 --> 00:37:34.616
From within you do not curse anyone,

00:37:34.818 --> 00:37:41.618
nor do you hanker after anything or
devour anyone. All these six enemies
get detached from within.

00:37:41.706 --> 00:37:47.616
The greatest Light of Spirit is that you
do not have to make any effort.

00:37:48.843 --> 00:37:54.073
They say that keep your mind under
control. There is no need. You do not
have to control anybody.

00:37:54.073 --> 00:37:57.412
As you keep growing deeper in your
Self-realized state,

00:37:57.412 --> 00:38:01.949
the darkness keeps getting eliminated
in that light.

00:38:02.700 --> 00:38:07.070
This is a very big gain and whoever has
not gained this benefit,

00:38:07.070 --> 00:38:12.805
he should know that his Self realization
has not fully matured.

00:38:12.805 --> 00:38:16.941
If our self realisation has matured
completely,

00:38:16.941 --> 00:38:22.724
then in our lives, in the society around
us, in our Sahaja Yoga community,

00:38:22.724 --> 00:38:30.562
everywhere, a new type of person
should develop,

00:38:30.562 --> 00:38:37.817
who is identified with the Spirit, who is
overwhelmed by the Light of Spirit, in
whom one can have spiritual vision of
Shiva.

00:38:37.984 --> 00:38:43.994
Now you have seen Lord Shiva. When
Shiva got married, his wife

00:38:44.266 --> 00:38:52.736
was the sister of Vishnuji. Vishnuji
himself was Kubera(God of wealth).

00:38:52.946 --> 00:39:00.504
So it was Kubera’s sister whom He(Shri
Shiva) was marrying. He sat on his
Nandi(Shri Shiva’s bull),

00:39:00.504 --> 00:39:06.339
without any reins or anything, just
sitting astride with both legs spread
out

00:39:06.339 --> 00:39:10.550
and Nandi was coming, galloping and
He(Shri Shiva) sitting over it with very
little clothes on Him.

00:39:10.550 --> 00:39:17.097
All this is an expression that he had no
perseverance to anything,

00:39:17.097 --> 00:39:20.158
He had no thoughts that “I must have
this.”

00:39:20.158 --> 00:39:26.297
Otherwise, anyone would think, I am
marrying Kubera’s sister, “Which
clothes should I wear?

00:39:27.337 --> 00:39:31.507
In which chariot should I go?” Clothes
would be tailored ten days in advance,

00:39:31.507 --> 00:39:36.631
shoes selected, the whole appearance
prepared, then only He would go for His marriage.

00:39:36.729 --> 00:39:44.819
But Lord Shiva thought, I am getting
married, that’s all I know. He didn’t think
about anything else.

00:39:44.821 --> 00:39:48.531
He didn’t think about anything else.
And those who accompanied him

00:39:48.531 --> 00:39:53.405
were like him, some had only one eye,
some had their limbs deformed,

00:39:53.405 --> 00:39:55.953
yet he took them all along,
unconcerned.

00:39:55.953 --> 00:40:02.495
This symbolically means that when you
have the Light of the Spirit within you

00:40:03.078 --> 00:40:07.738
then you can have any deformity in
your body, anything,

00:40:08.124 --> 00:40:11.104
any type, any kind of funny face,

00:40:11.104 --> 00:40:17.097
but when you have that light, then
Shiva accepts you and takes you along
in His marriage procession.

00:40:17.265 --> 00:40:21.095
Everyone present was surprised,
wondering, what kind of groom is this

00:40:21.168 --> 00:40:24.064
riding on Nandi, legs spread aside on
two sides.

00:40:24.064 --> 00:40:27.723
But he was free spirited, inconsiderate,
and disinterested.

00:40:27.748 --> 00:40:34.248
People must have talked among
themselves, what kind of groom is
coming in this way?

00:40:34.248 --> 00:40:38.497
This was not liked by Shri Parvati,
because she knew

00:40:38.497 --> 00:40:46.504
that Her husband is the embodiment of
the pure spirit. That is why He is called
detached.

00:40:46.504 --> 00:40:54.284
In this two aspects of our own being
are revealed. One is on the outside, is
the Vishnu form

00:40:54.284 --> 00:41:00.101
and within is our Shiva form.

00:41:00.509 --> 00:41:09.849
We have to be like Shiva, free,
disinterested and detached.

00:41:09.849 --> 00:41:14.963
If we become the spirit then any kind of
attachment cannot be within us.

00:41:14.963 --> 00:41:22.139
Then outwardly, you may be Krishna or
anyone,

00:41:22.139 --> 00:41:26.742
but the Shiva within you shall remain
established.

00:41:26.956 --> 00:41:34.466
When you have become the Spirit form,
then the outer form does not remain
important anymore.

00:41:34.466 --> 00:41:40.309
Then your feelings for such things will
change completely.

00:41:40.309 --> 00:41:43.381
Then your feelings for such things will
change completely.

00:41:43.381 --> 00:41:51.192
There is a beautiful example of this
from Shri Eknath ji’s life, He once
carried the ‘kaawad’ ( vessel containing
holy water) all the way to Dwarka

00:41:51.192 --> 00:41:55.463
to offer water there after climbing up
the hill.

00:41:55.463 --> 00:41:59.689
He was deeply immersed in devotion.
Many people had gone along with him,
each carrying their ‘kaawad’ filled with
holy water.

00:42:00.485 --> 00:42:07.525
But there he saw a donkey, dying of
thirst

00:42:07.525 --> 00:42:10.278
and so he made him drink the water,
(which was meant to be offered to the
temple deity).

00:42:10.278 --> 00:42:17.583
People said, what are you doing? You
walked for so long carrying this vessel
filled with holy water and now you have
given it to this donkey?

00:42:18.099 --> 00:42:22.969
Eknath replied, don’t you know that my
Krishna Himself came down to drink
this water.

00:42:22.969 --> 00:42:29.867
Only a Realized Soul can understand
such subtle feelings of bhakti.

00:42:29.867 --> 00:42:33.961
Outwardly to say that we brought the
kaawad

00:42:33.961 --> 00:42:38.802
and we offered it to the deity. Who are
we?

00:42:39.037 --> 00:42:43.827
When this feeling breaks, when the
feeling of I’ness is not there,

00:42:43.827 --> 00:42:48.998
there was this poor thirsty creature
lying there and it was given the water
to drink,

00:42:48.998 --> 00:42:52.166
it’s all right, the Param Chaitanya has
done this work. Who are we in
this(work).

00:42:53.622 --> 00:42:58.282
That is why many things about saints
that we could not understand before,

00:42:58.282 --> 00:43:01.675
you will now be able to understand,
because now you have attained Self-
Realisation.

00:43:01.675 --> 00:43:03.662
You too will perform such deeds.

00:43:04.440 --> 00:43:08.160
The imprudence we had about these
saints,

00:43:08.367 --> 00:43:12.557
that their lives seemed insane to us
was because we ourselves were insane.

00:43:12.557 --> 00:43:16.572
When you go to a lunatic asylum, even
a sane person appears mad.

00:43:16.676 --> 00:43:21.496
In the same way they(saints) came into
this mad world and tried to make us
understand (the truth),

00:43:21.496 --> 00:43:26.759
but nobody understood them. Instead,
people troubled them and harassed
them

00:43:26.759 --> 00:43:31.256
because they were identified with the
spirit and established in Shiva tatwa, so
they were of the form of Shiva.

00:43:31.256 --> 00:43:37.076
Such a person who is established in
Shiv principle, he may live in whichever
way outwardly, but his Shiva principle

00:43:37.076 --> 00:43:39.953
manifests as light, it glows outside.

00:43:40.395 --> 00:43:46.415
The greatest thing is generosity. This
generosity is the power of Shiva

00:43:46.415 --> 00:43:56.714
Shiva is so generous hearted that he
gives boons even to demons.

00:43:58.408 --> 00:44:01.133
Why? Because He gives the boons.

00:44:01.133 --> 00:44:04.027
Now, some people come to me and ask,
Mother please give us boons.

00:44:04.027 --> 00:44:07.528
I know very well that these people are
very bad, still I say, alright you want
boons, here take it.

00:44:07.528 --> 00:44:13.245
The Param Chaitanya will take care of
them; what do I have to do?

00:44:14.719 --> 00:44:18.119
Even demons were granted boons,
come on you want it, here it is.

00:44:18.119 --> 00:44:21.946
come on you want it, here it is.
Absolutely generous,

00:44:21.950 --> 00:44:25.850
what you may call, blind generosity.

00:44:25.850 --> 00:44:29.463
But actually, it is not blind generosity
because there is complete faith that
Param Chaitanya is there,

00:44:29.463 --> 00:44:33.745
it is my power only and it is doing all
the work. I just say, take it.

00:44:33.745 --> 00:44:38.814
After taking it(the boons) from here, on
the way Lord Vishnu ruined
his(demon’s) condition.

00:44:39.685 --> 00:44:45.085
The one who knows everything, for him
there is no concern,

00:44:45.085 --> 00:44:49.102
what will happen to him or what will not
happen. He knows everything.

00:44:49.128 --> 00:44:54.948
Similarly, one who is established in Shiv
principle, he is completely content
within himself.

00:44:55.124 --> 00:45:00.914
He knows everything and understands
everything, but he will not say it.

00:45:01.286 --> 00:45:07.366
He knows everything. And the greatest
power of Shiva is love,

00:45:08.363 --> 00:45:17.693
power of love, in which there is no
expectation of return, no expectation of
return, unconditional love.

00:45:18.846 --> 00:45:26.146
His compassion is so powerful that you
will be surprised to see such compassion.

00:45:26.146 --> 00:45:31.317
Many people say to me, Mother, why
did you help that man? He is such a
bad person;

00:45:31.317 --> 00:45:37.080
he did this and that. Well, what can I
do? He came to me, so it happened –
let it be

00:45:37.080 --> 00:45:40.274
Whatever happened, happened, let it
go.

00:45:40.274 --> 00:45:43.797
It is compassion, what else can one do?
Who can stop it?

00:45:43.797 --> 00:45:48.442
When the whole body is filled with
compassion, then whoever comes near,

00:45:48.442 --> 00:45:53.375
this body will act through its
compassion. This body will not give up.
What can be done?

00:45:53.375 --> 00:45:58.838
Similarly, in a Self-realized person, the
power of compassion grows

00:45:59.178 --> 00:46:05.478
and it is so addictive that one does not
enjoy it alone. His very nature becomes
like this, that he becomes extremely
powerful.

00:46:05.478 --> 00:46:09.546
Once you become self realised, you
simply cannot sit quietly, no matter
what you do.

00:46:09.546 --> 00:46:13.026
You will feel alright, I have experienced
it – now let ten others drink this nectar,
then only we will enjoy.

00:46:13.026 --> 00:46:18.631
Let’s see, come along make this(man)
self realised, make that man self
realised.

00:46:19.171 --> 00:46:23.247
Let’s see, come along make this(man)
self realised, make that man
self realised.

00:46:23.247 --> 00:46:27.373
He will not face troubles. People will
harass you and speak ill of you.

00:46:27.373 --> 00:46:32.060
But it will not affect you at all, because
you have become

00:46:32.060 --> 00:46:35.462
like a brush in the hands of the Divine
Artist, the Param Chaitanya.

00:46:35.462 --> 00:46:39.451
He is not bothered. The artist knows it
all, what am I to do in this.

00:46:39.451 --> 00:46:44.299
I am just watching this picture being
created.

00:46:44.299 --> 00:46:53.795
Similarly, his nature is inherently
detached so that he becomes
immensely powerful.

00:46:53.805 --> 00:47:07.145
His fear and concerns all vanish and he
is able to do this beautiful works in a
very skillfully.

00:47:07.145 --> 00:47:09.087
People are amazed, how he did this.

00:47:09.234 --> 00:47:15.684
And he explains things so beautifully
that if someone has ego,

00:47:15.684 --> 00:47:18.322
he will never go and tell him directly
that you are very egoistic. Never.

00:47:18.322 --> 00:47:23.907
A Self-Realised person will never say
that. Not like some Sahaja Yogis tell
others, you have a Bhoot in you.

00:47:23.907 --> 00:47:30.063
One should not say that. Let me tell you
by an example of this, about Shri
Ramdas Swami.

00:47:30.332 --> 00:47:35.932
Once, Shivaji had a little pride, because
he was building a great fort

00:47:35.932 --> 00:47:38.795
and thousands of people were working
in it. He began to feel egoistically

00:47:38.795 --> 00:47:45.577
that I am sustaining so many people. At
that time Ramdas Swami arrived there,

00:47:45.577 --> 00:47:51.442
he used to appear wherever he was
required. He saw that he(Shivaji) had
become egoistic,

00:47:51.442 --> 00:47:54.454
but he didn’t say anything. Nearby
there was a large rock.

00:47:54.454 --> 00:47:56.414
Ramdas Swami said, break this rock
very slowly.

00:47:56.444 --> 00:48:01.414
As they kept breaking that, it became
smaller and smaller till about the size of
a coconut.

00:48:01.488 --> 00:48:04.748
He(Ramdas Swami) took that in his
hand and banged it on the ground.

00:48:04.748 --> 00:48:08.738
To everyone’s surprise, inside that rock
there was water and within the water
was a frog.

00:48:10.120 --> 00:48:14.650
At that moment, Shivaji immediately fell
at the feet of Ramdas Swami’s, realising
that the one who gives life,

00:48:14.650 --> 00:48:20.151
also provides you with water, then who
am I to think that I am the giver? How
he(Ramdas Swami) broke his(Shivaji’s)
ego!

00:48:20.151 --> 00:48:26.005
You will be surprised that even science
says that a frog can survive without air

00:48:26.005 --> 00:48:28.662
as long as it is in water.

00:48:32.014 --> 00:48:35.724
Now if you have to break someone’s
ego,

00:48:35.724 --> 00:48:38.418
you don’t have to tell him that you are
very egoistical.

00:48:39.883 --> 00:48:42.763
You only have to think that he is very
egoistical

00:48:42.763 --> 00:48:46.783
and then the Param Chaitanya will
arrange for that and will itself break his
ego.

00:48:48.444 --> 00:48:54.744
But first of all, a Realized soul has to
think that

00:48:54.774 --> 00:49:00.454
Now, I have surrendered myself to Lord
Shiva, I am surrendered to my Spirit.

00:49:00.538 --> 00:49:05.898
Because of my Spirit only this Param
Chaitanya is doing all this work

00:49:05.898 --> 00:49:11.939
and that is why I am not worried about
anything. Who can be my enemy?

00:49:11.982 --> 00:49:17.612
Who can kill me? I am living in the
supreme being.

00:49:17.612 --> 00:49:21.654
When he is doing everything, then what
am I doing?”

00:49:23.300 --> 00:49:30.200
When one has a feeling like this, then
one can say that we have recognized
Shiva within.

00:49:30.200 --> 00:49:34.207
We understand our outer being and all
else very well and also our dignity

00:49:34.207 --> 00:49:39.537
but we must recognise this Shiva which
is within us, which is in our innermost
being.

00:49:39.537 --> 00:49:46.914
The one who is the support of our
entire power, which we call as Sat-
Chit-Ananda,

00:49:46.914 --> 00:49:49.980
we should worship that Shiva.

00:49:50.213 --> 00:49:53.253
Eternal Blessings to You all.
